original_title: Tarja Turunen e Harus: In Concert - Live at Sibelius Hall
overview: Tarja Turunen & Harus - Live at Sibelius Hall is a collaboration album by Finnish soprano Tarja Turunen with musicians Kalevi Kiviniemi, Marzi Nyman and Markku Khron record at the Sibelius Hall, Finland and released on 25 November 2011.
